{"tid":391281,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"交友app識咗個肥婆","createTime":"2017-09-07T16:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T07:19:57.000Z","uid":125516,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7485dd15f536cfee20f4878b3deaf5e379071c5","tid":391281,"uid":125516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5f5194fb91b363b100011cdae8319580be278b","tid":391281,"uid":71712,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:01:51.000Z","msg":"教訓你未見過樣咪去得咁盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b94641547a17788a58356bbb275ce2462f8d97f","tid":391281,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:02:09.000Z","msg":"努力減肥就唔係肥婆啦"},{"pid":"31180f4efb4ec057fd634ba9f4b05a8ffbb71a07","tid":391281,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"咩apps <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c4f6a98212fe318767d007f91edc8f74408cc4","tid":391281,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"聽聲都知係咪肥婆喇"},{"pid":"c910b00efa70d3ced55b45662e847b4ae7f27bce","tid":391281,"uid":134864,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"大部份肥到成座山咁嘅肥婆，條頸後面都好多老泥，因為佢哋沖涼嘅時候卒唔到。 <br />\n老泥俾頸部脂肪一層層夾住，日復日年復年咁累積。 <br />\n所以大部份肥婆條頸都係黑色，越黑老泥越厚。 <br />\n如果你哋有幸溝到肥婆，就人一世物一世點都要試下。<br />\n首先用手指濕少少水起勢咁卒，用匙羹刮出嚟，加兩滴美極慢慢品嚐。 <br />\n初哥可能話核突，但你唔食肥婆老泥等於登上白雲山唔食山水豆腐花一樣咁傻的嗎。 <br />\n<br />\n下身方面又係有學問，肥婆食咁多漢堡包同牛肉，男性荷爾蒙分泌過盛。 <br />\n所以塊西至屎o全部都係毛，無論佢幾乾淨，都有陣咸魚溝變壞乳酪嘅味道。 <br />\n據英國研究，82.5%肥婆都唔會剃腳毛，因為烏低身嗰下等於做sit up，有違肥人忠旨。 <br />\n所以肥婆啲腳毛永遠好似鐵線咁粗。 <br />\n奶西嘅時候叫佢瞓低你忠個頭埋去，兩隻手要掃佢隻腳啲鐵線等佢起雞皮，然後叫佢嗰對火腿夾實自己個頭唔好比空氣流出。 <br />\n陣咸魚味喺真空環境會得到昇華，係有層次而漸進的。<br />\n奶嗰時攝攝聲，有3D立體音響加回音效果。 <br />\n你嗅覺，味覺，觸覺，聽覺得到前所未有嘅享受，呢啲先叫人生啊。 <br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪嗰part唔多講，因為肥婆塊田多肉好撞係常識，你塞咗入去會感受到溫暖同安全感，比一層一層肉緊緊包住。 <br />\n<br />\n成日笑肥婆以為自己好識食嗰啲人，根本就係未夠班，自以為是嘅表現。你比食女界嘅高手揀減肥前欣宜定係整容後楊怡，佢完全唔想答你，一嚟佢唔想笑勁你問無聊野，二嚟佢已經諗緊點班支美極返嚟。"},{"pid":"8a0dabf212d0698bacf3369b4671e368aec214cc","tid":391281,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905ca44c5636975f7667cefb1c83118fec09e386","tid":391281,"uid":16462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:06:24.000Z","msg":"記住帶美極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cba8dbfedae57c3ba9da79e49aab0d1eebb9d0","tid":391281,"uid":125516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>努力減肥就唔係肥婆啦</blockquote><br />\n佢真係好俾心機架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d2acbc670ba60f17cd5db709de36e4d78889fe","tid":391281,"uid":125516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽聲都知係咪肥婆喇</blockquote><br />\n把聲好好j架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eec707744235a1bb3da63ebb76ab714e9e1dfe0","tid":391281,"uid":59569,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽聲都知係咪肥婆喇</blockquote><br />\n把聲好好j架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fb58fb903b18ba2a1539a8a457e786b1b97cb5","tid":391281,"uid":125516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩apps <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec699