/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有人要喎 唔狗衝等幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6a630134232b0f48aebe92768cda60b99b6b51","tid":391281,"uid":125516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有幾肥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n150幾cm 60幾kg</blockquote><br />\n咁好快姐<br />\n如果五官幾好都投資得過</blockquote><br />\n就係五官唔係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c13488915edc86c9d3df23350e424d2e1e1d914","tid":391281,"uid":96497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有幾肥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n150幾cm 60幾kg</blockquote><br />\n死 我都差唔多接近有咁肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來已經俾人叫美極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9697b5e2add8b992c39328853f9151062515e0d","tid":391281,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有幾肥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n150幾cm 60幾kg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌我都係咁<br />\n原來咁樣已經叫美極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}